settings.local.json — permission reference
==========================================

CURRENT STATE
  Claude can stage files (git add) but must ask your approval before
  committing or pushing.

TO GRANT COMMIT + PUSH PERMISSION
  Add these two lines back into the "allow" array in settings.local.json:

    "Bash(git commit -m ' *)",
    "Bash(git push *)"

  Full file with all permissions enabled:

    {
      "permissions": {
        "allow": [
          "Bash(git add *)",
          "Bash(git commit -m ' *)",
          "Bash(git push *)"
        ]
      }
    }

TO REVOKE ALL PERMISSIONS
  Leave the "allow" array empty:

    {
      "permissions": {
        "allow": []
      }
    }

NOTE
  This file is for human reference only — Claude Code reads settings.local.json,
  not this file.
